feature | storage/filesystem | Add filesystem storage backend: read_cert(), write_cert(), list_certs(), write_key() for PEM file I/O
feature | acme/jws | Add josepy-based JWK generation, JWS signing, nonce validation, and DigiCert EAB credential injection
