feature | agent/nodes/retry_scheduler | Implement Phase 3 retry scheduler: exponential backoff with bounded retries, routes to next domain
feature | docker | Add Docker multi-stage build (unit tests + image), gated CI steps, docker-compose for Pebble integration tests
