feature | mcp_server | add read_cert_details tool: rich cert inspection per domain (subject CN, SANs, issuer org, detected CA, serial, not_before/not_after, days_until_expiry); _extract_cert_details helper uses cryptography.x509; locking test covers 5 read-only tools
